NetHack 5.0.0 is a version of the game NetHack released in May 2026.

This package can safely be installed alongside Slackware's system default copy of NetHack.

The working directory is /var/lib/nethack500.

This script builds with X11 support for tiles (for graphical gameplay in addition to regular ascii) and the .desktop file calls 'nethack -wx11'.
Slackware -current (and Slackware 15 64-bit) is capable of building with Qt (which is run with 'nethack -wqt').
To build with Qt support pass QT=TRUE option as follows: 'QT=TRUE ./nethack500.Slackbuild'